---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ServiceExplore from '../../components/ServiceExplore.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Dental Implants — Oasis Dental Care, Huntington Beach"
  description="Permanent dental implants in Huntington Beach. Dr. Jason Fu uses 3D imaging for precise, comfortable placement. Call (714) 893-2106."
  page="services"
>

<section class="phero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/services">Services</a><span class="sep">/</span><span style="color:#cfe6e2">Dental Implants</span></div>
    <span class="tag">Restorative dentistry</span>
    <h1>Dental Implants</h1>
    <p>A permanent solution that looks, feels, and functions like a real tooth.</p>
    <div class="acts">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book a consultation <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pad">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="split">
      <div>

        <div class="img-ph reveal">
          <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
          <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
          <span class="img-ph-desc">Confident patient with full smile in natural light</span>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal">
          <span class="tag">Overview</span>
          <h2>Reclaim your smile—for life.</h2>
          <p>If you're missing one or more teeth, dental implants offer a permanent, secure solution. As a leading implant provider in Huntington Beach, we combine expertise with cutting-edge technology.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <h3>What Is a Dental Implant?</h3>
          <p>A titanium post is placed in the jawbone and acts as an artificial tooth root. A custom crown is attached on top. Implants look, feel, and function like your natural teeth—and can last a lifetime with proper care.</p>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Implant diagram or side-by-side comparison with gap</span>
          </div>

          <h3>Who Is a Good Candidate?</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Adults with one or more missing teeth</li>
            <li>Patients with adequate jawbone density</li>
            <li>Non-smokers or those willing to quit</li>
            <li>People looking for a permanent alternative to dentures or bridges</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>The Process</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>3D imaging and personalized treatment plan</li>
            <li>Implant placement (in-office procedure)</li>
            <li>Healing period (osseointegration)</li>
            <li>Custom crown fabrication and final placement</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">3D imaging in use, or Dr. Fu reviewing scan with patient</span>
          </div>

          <h3>Why Implants Over Alternatives?</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Preserve jawbone and prevent bone loss</li>
            <li>No removal or adhesives needed</li>
            <li>Do not affect neighboring teeth</li>
            <li>Designed to last decades</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <span class="tag">Common questions</span>
          <h2 class="prose" style="margin-top:8px">Good to know.</h2>
          <div class="faq">
            <details open><summary>Does getting an implant hurt?</summary><p>Placement is done with local anesthesia and comfort options, so the procedure itself is comfortable. Most patients manage any post-treatment soreness with over-the-counter pain relief.</p></details>
            <details><summary>How long do dental implants last?</summary><p>With good oral hygiene and regular checkups, implants are designed to last a lifetime. The crown on top may eventually need replacement after many years of normal wear.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Will my insurance help cover it?</summary><p>Many plans cover part of implant treatment. We'll verify your benefits before you start and give you a clear, written estimate—no surprises.</p></details>
            <details><summary>How long is the whole process?</summary><p>It varies by case, but most implants take a few months from placement to final crown to allow proper healing. We'll give you a personalized timeline at your consultation.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Am I too old for dental implants?</summary><p>Age alone is rarely a limiting factor. We'll evaluate your bone density and overall health to determine candidacy. Many patients in their 70s and 80s are excellent candidates.</p></details>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <aside>
        <div class="scard reveal">
          <div class="hd"><div class="grid-ov"></div><h3>Book your implant consult</h3><p>Same-week appointments often available</p></div>
          <div class="bd">
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg><span>Consults typically 45–60 min</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg><span>Most insurance accepted &amp; verified up front</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 11 4.5-2 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg><span>3D-guided, comfort-focused care</span></div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <a class="btn" href="/contact">Schedule an Implant Consultation</a>
            <a class="btn btn-out" href="tel:7148932106" style="justify-content:center">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<ServiceExplore />

</Layout>
